核心能力 Competence
■ 職能治療專業知識與理論
具備職能治療專業知識理論基礎，以為專業技能奠基。 Professional Knowledge and Theories of Occupational Therapy
Acuire Professional Knowledge and Theories of Occupational Therapy in order to Develop Therapeutic Skills□ 職能治療專業技能
具備職能治療專業技能，以提供個案職能表現之評估、分析與治療的能力。 Occupational Therapy Therapeutic Skills
Acuire Occupational Therapy Therapeutic Skills to Provide Evaluation, Analysis and Intervention for Clients' Occupational Performance□ 溝通表達及團隊合作之能力
培養適切溝通表達及團隊合作能力，以建立良好的醫病關係及專業團隊互動。 Communication and Interdisciplinary Cooperation Abilities
Acuire Communication Proficiency and Interdisciplinary Cooperation Abilities in order to Establish Therapeutic Relationship and Improve Professional Team Interacttion□ 獨立思考及問題解決之能力
培養具有獨立思考、臨床推理及問題解決的能力，並能終身學習。 Indipendent Critical Thinking and Problem Solving Abilities
Cultivate Indipendent Critical Thinking, Clinical Reasoning and Problem Solving Abilities, and Develop Lifelong Learning□ 創新與領導能力
培養具有創新與領導的能力，以為專業技能或研究奠基。 Innovative and Leadership Abilities
Cultivate Innovative and Leadership Abilities in order to Develop Therapeutic Skills and Professional Research 

課程概述 Course Description
       簡介職能治療的理論架構，討論理論架構應用原則以及對於各類情境的介入觀點。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    Students will be able to
1. Link an individual’s participation in occupational areas with his/her component skills and the contextual factors
2. Understand the meaning of occupation and the theoretical knowledge applied to maximize one’s meaningful engagement in his/her life.
3. Recognize theories/frame of reference for potential use in practice.
     

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Course orientation2Occupation and Occupational Science3The Occupational Therapy Process 4The Occupational Therapy Process 5Theories Derived from Learning Perspectives EHP model6Theories Derived from Learning Perspectives 7Rehabilitation Perspectives: Biomechanical & Rehabilitative FOR 8Rehabilitation Perspectives: Biomechanical & Rehabilitative FOR 9Midterm exam10Midterm report11OT實務模式與參考架構 OT practice model and frame of reference (FOR)12OT實務模式與參考架構 OT practice model and frame of reference (FOR)13Person-environment-occupation model (PEO model)14EHP model15Model of Human Occupation 16Model of Human Occupation 17Final exam18Final report 

